Game Notes

Unforeseen Incidents is a classical style interactive mystery set in a
beautifully hand-painted world. When small-town handyman Harper Pendrell
meets a dying woman in the street, he unwittingly stumbles into a diabolical
conspiracy - a mystery only he can solve. An unknown disease is spreading
across the country, and between them a scientist, a reporter and a reclusive
artist hold the key to stopping it
